WESTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
NEW JERSEY TO BERMUDA.
33 FOOT VESSEL MIGRAINE 2, ONE PERSON ON BOARD,
OVERDUE ATLANTIC HIGHLANDS (40-24N 074-01W) TO
BERMUDA (32-17N 064-47W). VESSELS IN VICINITY
REQUESTED TO KEEP A SHARP LOOKOUT, ASSIST
IF POSSIBLE. REPORTS TO RCC BOSTON,
PHONE: 617 223 8555, E-MAIL: RCCBOSTON@USCG.MIL.
